<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.4.4">
<l>pariya viraṇiyaṉa tāka maṇiyukirāl</l>
<l>ariyuruvāyk kīṇṭā ṉaruḷtanta vānamakku</l>
<l>porutiraikaḷ pōntulavu pullāṇi kaitoḻutēṉ</l>
<l>arimalarkkaṇ ṇīrtatumpa vantukilum nillāvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[Ah!] The way that he, who in a lion form with glittering claws,</l>
<l>Split Hiraṇya’s thick chest, grants us grace! I worship, hands [joined],</l>
<l>In Pullāṇi, where colliding waves wander, returning back [and forth],</l>
<l>As tears overflow [my] streaked flower[-like] eyes; my fine clothes</l>
<l rend="indent">will not stay put.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
